docs/working/CONTEXT.md:24:9. Compliance dashboards, statutory registers, audit logs, reports, and member portal self-service.
docs/working/CONTEXT.md:27:Source docs recommend a modular-monolith backend, Django/Python, PostgreSQL, JWT auth, service-layer business logic, REST APIs, audit events, and external adapters for SAP, bank/payment, email/SMS, CDSL, and file storage. The current codebase is only the frontend prototype.
